<tr id="L455"><td><a href="#L455">455</a></td><td>KIRK:  Indeed it shall, Mister Spock. Ironic, isn't it? Way back in the 20th century, the H-Bomb was the ultimate weapon, their doomsday machine, and we used something like it to destroy another doomsday machine. Probably the first time such a weapon has ever been used for constructive purposes.</td></tr>

<tr id="L456"><td><a href="#L456">456</a></td><td>SPOCK:  Appropriate, Captain. However, I can't help wondering if there are any more of those weapons wandering around the universe.</td></tr>

